<concept xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="topic_2_3_3">
   <title>Pod Options</title>
   <conbody>
    <p>Whenever you hover the mouse over each pod a pop-up menu is displayed that allows you to
      perform the following actions on the specific pod, as shown in the figure.</p>
    <ul id="ul_il1_wtl_zx">
      <li>Toggle Axis Labels—Allows you to toggle the items displayed on the X and Y axis.</li>
      <li>Toggle Data Labels—Allows you to display values on the Y axis on the pie chart. </li>
      <li>
        <p>Toggle 3D View of the chart—Allows you to switch between the three dimensional and two
          dimensional views of the charts.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Print pod using browser printing to a local printer</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Export pod to JPEG, PNG, or PDF formats</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>View original report</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Toggle the grid on and off to gain a larger view of the chart</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>Toggle the chart on and off to gain a larger view of the grid.</p>
        <fig><title>Figure 1-11: Export Pod</title><image href="./media/Image_037.png" placement="break" scale="50" id="image_kl1_wtl_zx"/></fig>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </conbody>
</concept>
